      <p>There is nothing more rewarding than seeing a Bride on her wedding day looking beautiful, confident, and effortlessly radiant. I take great pride in creating a bespoke look, for every Bride that I have the honour of working with.</p>
      <p>On the consultation trial before the big day I will create a detailed plan of skincare products, depending on skin type, for a long-lasting base. Then, working with you, I discuss styles and make-up looks that reflect your wedding and importantly, your personality. Each Bride is unique, and your makeup should express this!</p>
      <p class="no-margin">I use some of the best luxury products such as Giorgio Armani, Charlotte Tilbury, Dior, Lancôme, NARS, Bobbi Brown, MAC, and many others!</p>

      <h3>Pricing</h3>
