      <br/>
      <q>Donna came and did my make up trial and she was so lovely and professional, she did exactly what I wanted which was just a natural look. But one that lasted! She did such a gorgeous job I used her again before my wedding to do my make up for a friends wedding.<br/>Donna was absolutely brilliant in my wedding day, she made me feel totally comfortable and the make up was flawless. I loved having Donna here on the day. She was absolutely lovely from start to finish, no fuss. Which was exactly what I needed! Thank you so much Donna.</q><figcaption>Sophie Broome</figcaption>
